nl.inl.blacklab.search.sequences

Class SpansInBucketsPerDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.inl.blacklab.search.sequences.SpansInBucketsPerDocument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SpansInBuckets
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SpansInBucketsPerDocumentSorted

    public class SpansInBucketsPerDocument
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrap a Spans to retrieve matches per document, so we can process all matches in a document efficiently. This way we can retrieve hits per document and perform some operation on them (like sorting or retrieving some extra information). Afterwards we can use HitsPerDocumentSpans to convert the per-document hits into a normal Spans object again.
